channel.title: How do you Change were you spawn?
channel.description: Hi guys, Ive been coding servers for over a year.. and ive never found out how to change were you spawn when you first join the server. I've changed the home place and need to know how to change the spawnpoint.. Could anyone help me please? -Nick

item.title: How do you Change were you spawn?
item.dc:creator: @deery50 deery50
item.description:
@deery50 wrote:

go to playerhandler and find the cordanates that you already spawn at and replace them with the ones you want to spawn at.
